OL,3,CStrangers rescue baby from burning car
OL,4,Cas mother screamed in horror
OL,6,FWhen two men pulled over to help a
OL,7,Fwoman whose car was on fire, they soon
OL,8,Frealised her 10-month-old baby was
OL,9,Ftrapped inside, and without a second
OL,10,Fthought, they dove into the car which
OL,11,Fwas engulfed in flames to rescue the
OL,12,Fchild.
OL,14,FWes Beynon and his uncle Mark had been
OL,15,Ftravelling along the A465 Heads of the
OL,16,FValleys road towards Merthyr Tydfil
OL,17,Fwhen they noticed a distressed woman
OL,18,Fstood on the hard shoulder with smoke
OL,19,Fcoming from her car. They pulled over
OL,20,Fand soon realised her baby was trapped
OL,21,Finside.
