OL,3,CStrangers rescue baby from burning car
OL,4,Cas mother screamed in horror
OL,6,F"Me and my uncle Mark saw a young
OL,7,Fgirl, probably in her early to mid 20s
OL,8,Fby the passenger door, she appeared to
OL,9,Fbe distressed," Wes said. "I thought,
OL,10,Fwell, you know, that's not a safe
OL,11,Fplace to be, so I pulled into the exit.
OL,13,F"Myself and my uncle both jumped out
OL,14,Fof my vehicle, and I started running
OL,15,Fdown to her, because you could see
OL,16,Fflames coming out of the side of the
OL,17,Fbonnet, and up to the centre of the
OL,18,Fbonnet.
