OL,3,CStrangers rescue baby from burning car
OL,4,Cas mother screamed in horror
OL,6,F"She was screaming that her baby is in
OL,7,Fthe car. She was trying to open the
OL,8,Fpassenger the door, but it was clearly
OL,9,Flocked or jammed shut.
OL,11,F"I ran around to the driver's door,
OL,12,Fopened it, climbed in, and pushed the
OL,13,Fpassenger door open with help from my
OL,14,Funcle who was outside the vehicle.
OL,16,F"I unclipped the baby, and my uncle
OL,17,Fthen pulled the baby out the passenger
OL,18,Fseat. 30 seconds to one minute later,
OL,19,Fit would have been a different story.
OL,20,FSo you can obviously understand it.
