OL,3,CStrangers rescue baby from burning car
OL,4,Cas mother screamed in horror
OL,6,F"All the engine bay, the bonnet,
OL,7,Feverything was on fire. Me and Mark
OL,8,Fsort of worked together as a team,
OL,9,Fquite naturally, without thinking.
OL,11,F"The mother, her name is Alex, was
OL,12,Fdistraught, as you'd imagine. We got
OL,13,Fout of the way of the fire and you
OL,14,Fcould hear mighty bangs and smashing
OL,15,Fsounds from the glass."
OL,17,FAlex and Wez then phoned the emergency
OL,18,Fservices, and directed traffic into
OL,19,Fthe fast lane to keep things moving.
