OL,3,CStrangers rescue baby from burning car
OL,4,Cas mother screamed in horror
OL,6,F"I would do the same thing for someone
OL,7,Felse again tomorrow, because I hope
OL,8,Fthat if I was in that position,
OL,9,Fsomebody would do it for me," Wes
OL,10,Fadded.
OL,12,F"A lot of people would look at me in
OL,13,Fmy appearance - I am covered in
OL,14,Fpiercings and tattoos, I'm a
OL,15,Fmotorcycle club member - and say, 'oh,
OL,16,Fhe's trouble', you know? But I guess
OL,17,Fthis just goes to show, people should
OL,18,Fnever judge a book by its cover."
